### Merchant Admin Verification API Tests
### Requires JWT token for admin user

@host = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get all merchants pending approval
# @name getPendingMerchants
GET {{host}}/merchants/admin/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Approve a merchant
# @name approveMerchant
POST {{host}}/merchants/admin/{{merchantId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Reject a merchant with reason
# @name rejectMerchant
POST {{host}}/merchants/admin/{{merchantId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rejectionReason": "Documentación incompleta. Por favor suba su patente comercial."
}

###

### Suspend an active merchant
# @name suspendMerchant
POST {{host}}/merchants/admin/{{merchantId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "suspensionReason": "Quejas de clientes pendientes de revisión."
}

###

### Reactivate a suspended merchant
# @name reactivateMerchant
POST {{host}}/merchants/admin/{{merchantId}}/reactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
